  "text": "Example 3 (Bound in the parameter space of interest). For K = 1000, τ s = 1 sec, L = 1000 bits, W = 1 MHz and no fading, the bound given by (48) is ≈ 2, i.e., it is guaranteed that the transmit power under equal resource allocation is no more than around 3 dB worse than the optimal power. In [CITATION_1] we have numerically shown that the actual gap is much smaller.",
